events.name: Command Run
events.description: Fired when a CLI command is started.

___is_ci.description: Whether or not typewriter is currently running in a CI environment or not.

___command.description: The command name that was started.

___tracking_plan.description: Metadata about the Tracking Plan that typewriter was fired on.

___duration.description: The time taken to execute this command, in ms.

___client.description: Metadata about the client that typewriter is generating.

___token_method.description: Where the API token was fetched from.

events.name: Error Fired
events.description: Fired when an error is encountered.

___unexpected.description: Whether or not this error was an expected (and therefore, properly handled) error.

___is_ci.description: Whether or not typewriter is currently running in a CI environment or not.

___command.description: The command name that was started.

___tracking_plan.description: Metadata about the Tracking Plan that typewriter was fired on.

___client.description: Metadata about the client that typewriter is generating.

___token_method.description: Where the API token was fetched from.
